condition.narrative: Ensure that it follows the Rehabilitation Plan agreed with MOF in order to secure the end of the rehabilitation regime procedure ofthe PIE by the end of the third quarter of Fiscal Year 2020, and that a copy of the court decision confirming the end of therehabilitation regime procedure of the PIE is submitted to the Bank within one month of its issuance.
Ensure that the PIE and EnergoTrans have no cash deficit by the end of Fiscal Year 2020.

Prepare by the end of the second quarter of Fiscal Year 2020 and thereafter implement, under terms satisfactory to the Bank, a DebtManagement Strategy, which includes specific financial targets, acceptable to the Bank, and shall not amend or modify anyprovisions of said Strategy without the prior approval of the Bank.
